<paragraph blockId="4.[118,768,687,777]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">
Part of the gathering 
<emphasis box="[394,542,687,711]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">Hassler 8237</emphasis>
was later (
<bibRefCitation author="HASSLER" firstAuthor="HASSLER" page="69" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" pagination="66 - 71" refId="ref6666" refString="HASSLER, E. (1910). Ex herbario Hassleriano: Novitates paraguarienses. V. Bombacaceae. Repert. Spec. Nov. Regni Veg. 8: 66 - 71." type="journal article" year="1910">HASSLER, 1910: 69</bibRefCitation>
) used as 
<typeStatus box="[307,352,720,744]" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">type</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName box="[386,720,720,744]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="4" pageNumber="97" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="marginatum" variety="intermedium">
<emphasis box="[386,540,720,744]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">B. marginatum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[589,720,720,744]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">intermedium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see below) as 
<emphasis box="[227,417,753,777]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">Hassler 8237 p.p.</emphasis>
(i.e. 
<emphasis box="[472,570,753,777]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="97">pro parte</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
